@Marginalia.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5279

### Upload a Word document
POST {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documents/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.docx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document

< ./test.docx
------FormBoundary--

### Paste text as document
POST {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documents/paste
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is a sample manuscript text for analysis.",
  "filename": "draft.txt"
}

### Get document by ID
GET {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get suggestions for a document
GET {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/suggestions
Accept: application/json

### Trigger AI analysis
POST {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/documents/{{documentId}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentId": "{{documentId}}",
  "userInstructions": "Focus on expanding compressed narratives",
  "toneGuidance": "professional but warm"
}

### Create a new session
POST {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/sessions
Accept: application/json

### Get LLM config
GET {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/config/llm
Accept: application/json

### Update LLM config
PUT {{Marginalia.Api_HostAddress}}/api/config/llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endpoint": "https://your-account.services.ai.azure.com/openai/deployments/gpt-4o",
  "apiKey": "your-api-key",
  "modelName": "gpt-4o"
}

###
